  "texts": [
    "In the primary setting, each prediction is evaluated against a gold label using a three-way classification scheme: \"Yes\", \"To some extent\", and \"No\".",
    "Let C denote the set of all classes, and F 1 c the F1 score for class c ∈ C. The macro-F1 score is computed as the unweighted average across all classes:",
    "This metric penalizes class imbalance and rewards systems that maintain recall across minority classes such as \"To some extent\".",
    "Lenient Evaluation.",
    "To account for pedagogical similarity between \"Yes\" and \"To some extent\", the task also includes a two-way lenient evaluation protocol."
  ],
